::KitKat::

She gasped as she watched him drop to the floor. "ON MATRIX NO!" She 
tried to pick him up, but he was to heavy. She opened the room up and 
dragged him down the hall.  She finally got him to the lab and 
straiend herself getting him into a CR chamber. She turned the CR on 
and set it to maximum heal.  She sat down and called Drillbit on her 
link. "Can I please see you for a moment in the lab." she sat there, 
staring at the wall in complete shock.  This was getting to be a bit 
much for her to deal with at once like this.
